<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ a qiú nǐ lái dào wǒ men zhōng jiān 迦南14</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a qiú nǐ lái dào wǒ men zhōng jiān, ràng wǒ men jiàn dào nǐ de róng guāng.
 kāi qǐ wǒ men de yǎn jīng hé xīn qiào, cái néng biàn rèn fāng xiàng.
 wéi yǒu nǐ shì shén shì zhēn shén shì huó shén, shì yǒng yuǎn de wáng.
 zhǔ a qiú nǐ lái dào wǒ men zhōng jiān, bǎ wǒ men de xīn zhào liàng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>14</hymn_number>
</song>